MerchAccPaymentMethodSet.name: MerchAccPaymentMethodSet
MerchAccPaymentMethodSet.description: Defines an ordered list of payment methods that are available to a merchant's cudstomer during checkout. You can configure multiple payment method sets, each designated for a specific locale, payment region, or sale channel.

CurrencyIsoCode.description: Available only for organizations with the multicurrency feature enabled. The ISO code for any currency allowed by the organization.

DeveloperName.description: Unique name for the object given by the Payments admin.

PaymentMethodSummary.description: Summary field that is automatically populated with comma-separated values from MerchAccPaymentMethodType.
